2\t\n    33\t#### 验收标准\n    34\t> 以上验收标准的完整 Gherkin 用例详见 `tests
/bdd/matching.feature`。\n    35\t\n    36\t```gherkin\n    37\tFeature: Card Re
commendations\n    38\t  Scenario: User sees recommendation cards\n    39\t    G
iven the user is on the home screen with a complete profile\n    40\t    And the
re are 20 eligible candidates nearby\n    41\t    When the app requests GET /mat
ching/recommendations\n    42\t    Then the user should receive a stack of up to
